title: Vordere Brandjochspitze
description: The peak in the center-right of the photo is Vordere Brandjochspitze. Standing at 2,559m (8,396 ft) tall is one of the highest peaks in the Karwendel mountain range. The smaller peak to the left is Hechenberg at 1,943m (6,374ft) tall. View this photo on my blog here.
